✨ Rule of Thumb

File Type	Function Style	    Export Type
Screens	    Arrow Function	    Named Export ✅  rnfe 
Components	Arrow Function	    Named Export ✅
Hooks	    Arrow Function	    Named Export ✅
Utils	    Arrow or Reg. Func	Named Export ✅
Providers	Arrow Function	    Default Export ✅
Layout	    Arrow Function	    Default Export ✅